      "animated": false,
      "svgContent": "<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"420\" height=\"350\"><defs><linearGradient id=\"bg\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"0%\" y2=\"100%\"><stop offset=\"0%\" style=\"stop-color:#E3F2FD\"/><stop offset=\"100%\" style=\"stop-color:#BBDEFB\"/></linearGradient></defs><rect width=\"420\" height=\"350\" fill=\"url(#bg)\" rx=\"12\"/><text x=\"210\" y=\"25\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1565C0\">Pumping Lemma for Context-Free Languages</text><!-- String division visualization --><rect x=\"60\" y=\"60\" width=\"300\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#2196F3\" rx=\"5\"></rect><text x=\"210\" y=\"85\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">\n    String s = uvxyz\n    \n  </text><!-- Division markers --><line x1=\"120\" y1=\"55\" x2=\"120\" y2=\"105\" stroke=\"#1565C0\" stroke-width=\"2\"></line><line x1=\"180\" y1=\"55\" x2=\"180\" y2=\"105\" stroke=\"#1565C0\" stroke-width=\"2\"></line><line x1=\"240\" y1=\"55\" x2=\"240\" y2=\"105\" stroke=\"#1565C0\" stroke-width=\"2\"></line><line x1=\"300\" y1=\"55\" x2=\"300\" y2=\"105\" stroke=\"#1565C0\" stroke-width=\"2\"></line><!-- Division labels --><text x=\"90\" y=\"120\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1565C0\">\n    u\n    \n  </text><text x=\"150\" y=\"120\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1565C0\">\n    v\n    \n  </text><text x=\"210\" y=\"120\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1565C0\">\n    x\n    \n  </text><text x=\"270\" y=\"120\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1565C0\">\n    y\n    \n  </text><text x=\"330\" y=\"120\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1565C0\">\n    z\n    \n  </text><!-- Pumping arrows --><path d=\"M150 140 C150 160, 270 160, 270 140\" stroke=\"#1565C0\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" fill=\"none\"></path><polygon points=\"270,140 274,137 274,143\" fill=\"#1565C0\"></polygon><text x=\"210\" y=\"170\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1565C0\">\n    Pump v and y\n    \n  </text><!-- Conditions box --><rect x=\"60\" y=\"200\" width=\"300\" height=\"120\" fill=\"#64B5F6\" rx=\"5\"></rect><text x=\"210\" y=\"220\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">\n    Conditions:\n    \n  </text><!-- Condition 1 --><text x=\"80\" y=\"245\" text-anchor=\"start\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">\n    1. |vxy| ≤ p (pumping length)\n    \n  </text><!-- Condition 2 --><text x=\"80\" y=\"265\" text-anchor=\"start\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">\n    2. |vy| ≥ 1 (non-empty)\n    \n  </text><!-- Condition 3 --><text x=\"80\" y=\"285\" text-anchor=\"start\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">\n    3. uvⁱxyⁱz ∈ L for all i ≥ 0\n    \n  </text><!-- Conclusion --><text x=\"210\" y=\"320\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"10\" font-style=\"italic\" fill=\"#1565C0\">\n    If any condition fails, language is not context-free\n    \n  </text></svg>",
